Daylon Claasen has been a permanent feature for Maritzburg United this season - he also established himself when he recently netted a brace against Kaizer Chiefs in the league. The 47 year-old Silent is Claasen's UNCLE and they are both from Klerksdorp. "Brandon "Sgcebezana" Silent was a darling and a favourite of the Orlando Pirates supporters in the 1990s. He was a box-to-box player who ran the whole 90 minutes nonstop. Many still Sgcebezana's duels with Kaizer Chiefs dribbling wizard Doctor "16 Valve" Khumalo.  